title: The Sauna DMer - Machinima
description:
FREELY AVAILABLE CONTENT

The Sauna DMer

"The Sauna DMer" is is the epic story of Oily-Pecker Lehthineen (dimits) and his experiences with me, Daeman and other people. As he continues to disregard humanity and interpersonal relations while tending to his bookreading, he is slowly dragged into the web of a shadowy Vietnamese conspiracy originating with familial origins on dimits' side.

From SAMP Machinima to dub of obscure anime film, dimits and his adventures cast him to an entertaining experience.

Will he ever discover the purpose of it all?
